Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,地方检察官给出的交易是有期徒刑一年\N{\fs12}That's the deal the D.A's offering. One year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,二级性侵犯\N{\fs12}Second degree sexual assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我本以为我们可以胜诉\N{\fs12}l thought you said we could win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你担心你的妻子和女儿\N{\fs12}l know you're worried about your wife and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是判刑一年总好过十年\N{\fs12}But one year in jail is a lot better than ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂在哪\N{\fs12}So where's Marty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他退休了  法林先生  他让我问候您\N{\fs12}He's retiring, Mr. Fallin. He sends his regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,肯  这是我儿子尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}Oh, Ken, this is my son Nicholas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 很高兴认识你\N{\fs12}- Hi. - Um, pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,马蒂离开了 我很遗憾\N{\fs12}Well, I'm sorry to hear that Marty's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们合作有三十年了\N{\fs12}He, uh, he had our account for thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  有一个小问题\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin, we have a slight problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们额外给您增加的一 百万信贷额度两周前已经到期了\N{\fs12}That extra million we extended on your credit facility was due two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我们没有任何问题  只是在等收完账\N{\fs12}Well, we're good for that. We're just waiting for some  receivables.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言  这也不是我们的问题\N{\fs12}With all due respect, that's not our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肯  作为一个新手  我很欣赏你\N{\fs12}Ken, I appreciate that you're new with the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,想要给老板留下好印象\N{\fs12}Wanna impress the bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  呃 强迫客户在我们这儿行不通\N{\fs12}But, uh... we're not exactly in the game of strong-arming our clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  我的上司派我来\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin, my bosses sent me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上是他们不愿意参与到这个\N{\fs12}Truth of the matter is, they don't want to be in the business
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为欠款的客户提供融资的业务中\N{\fs12}of financing your delinquent clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我们能在周末之前处理完这件事\N{\fs12}l hope we can take care of this by the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  呃  替我给马蒂问好\N{\fs12}Yeah, well, uh... Say hi to Marty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  他有一点说的是对的\N{\fs12}Well, he has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我们不能再放任这些人了\N{\fs12}l mean, we can't keep Ietting these people slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是我们的老客户  尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}They're old clients, Nicholas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们欠我们一百万美元\N{\fs12}They owe us a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友杰德·托宾也在这些人中\N{\fs12}Your friend Jed Tobin is one of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟他说他已经晚六个月了吗\N{\fs12}You want to tell him he's six months late?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  看这个新的木星推杆\N{\fs12}Hey, Nick. Did you see this new Jupiter putter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有  - 碳素钢身  完美的平衡\N{\fs12}- No. - Carbon steel. Perfectly balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,设计者是有史以来最顶级的推杆设计师之一\N{\fs12}The guy that designed it is like one of the top putter designers of all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,太丑了\N{\fs12}lt's very ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:01:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你打过奥克芒吗  - 没有\N{\fs12}- You ever play Oakmont? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想打吗  - 并不怎么想\N{\fs12}- You want to? - Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不  尼克  木星公司的人已经安排好了\N{\fs12}No, Nick. No, the guys from Jupiter have set it up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,作为对我们这段时间认真工作的答谢\N{\fs12}as a thank-you for all the good work we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那你去吧\N{\fs12}Oh, you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  是奥克芒啊\N{\fs12}Nick. Oakmont!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还需要队友  阿尔文·马斯特森说他打得也不错\N{\fs12}lf you need a fourth, Alvin Masterson says he's a decent golfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文吗  那家伙打的太差了\N{\fs12}Alvin? That guy's got a terrible slice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,去几楼  哥儿们\N{\fs12}What floor, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,五楼\N{\fs12}5.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服不错\N{\fs12}That's a nice suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不喜欢有人在电梯里跟我聊天\N{\fs12}l don't like it either when people talk to me in an elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在这做什么  - 什么\N{\fs12}- What are you doing here? - Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你  是他\N{\fs12}Not you. Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 路易莎  - 请出去\N{\fs12}- Louisa. - Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想和你说几句话\N{\fs12}l just... I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧给我滚出去\N{\fs12}Get the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃  先生  你  - 别管闲事\N{\fs12}- Uh... sir, you... you... - Stay outta this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他走了吗\N{\fs12}ls he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  你还好吗\N{\fs12}Yeah. You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还好  呃  卢卡斯·法尔在你的办公室  他二十岁\N{\fs12}Yeah. Uh... in your office. Lucas Farr. He's twenty years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天社会服务部门把他弟弟接走了\N{\fs12}Social Services took his younger brothers out of his care yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以来参加今天下午的听证会\N{\fs12}So the shelter hearing's this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人  怎么回事\N{\fs12}Yeah... uh... this guy... what...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是我爸爸\N{\fs12}lt's my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事  先忙了\N{\fs12}I've got a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈三年前死于癌症\N{\fs12}My mother died three years ago-- cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  呃  我爸爸一直都不在\N{\fs12}And, uh... my dad's been gone forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就只剩下我和两个弟弟\N{\fs12}So it's just me and my two brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  昨天晚上有人敲门\N{\fs12}So... Iast night there's this knock at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,之后社会服务部门的人就带着一个警察进来了\N{\fs12}and some woman from Social Services comes in with a cop,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们带走了约翰和格伦\N{\fs12}and they take John and Glenn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,据说你把你的弟弟们锁在房间里\N{\fs12}Says here you locked your brothers in the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出去工作  总没办法一直找人照顾他们吧\N{\fs12}Well, I can't always find people to look after them when I go to work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那你在哪里工作\N{\fs12}Where do you work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在巴基的咖啡店  在北街\N{\fs12}At Bucky's Coffee. It's on the North Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这上面说  你弟弟在房间里玩烟花\N{\fs12}lt says that your brothers were lighting fireworks inside the apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还从五楼的窗户扔燃烧的纸团\N{\fs12}and dropping burning rolls of toilet paper from the fifth story window.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那应该是格伦  他会有一些小毛病\N{\fs12}That would be Glenn. He's got some problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他在一所特殊学校上学\N{\fs12}He's enrolled in a special needs school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是反应迟钝\N{\fs12}He's not retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是在阅读上有一些障碍\N{\fs12}He's just got problems with reading, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是注意力的问题\N{\fs12}lt's attention stum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  很明显你不能把他们锁在屋子里\N{\fs12}Well, clearly you can't lock them in an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这也不安全\N{\fs12}lt's just not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的  好吧  我又不傻\N{\fs12}l know that, okay? l mean, I'm not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只是  我必须工作\N{\fs12}lt's just... I have to go to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我现在雇不起保姆\N{\fs12}and I cannot amord to pay a babysitter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  下午会有一个关于监护权的听证会\N{\fs12}Well, there's a shelter hearing this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们试试看能不能解决这个问题\N{\fs12}We'll see what we can try and work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那些社会服务部门的人\N{\fs12}Listen, these guys from Social Services
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一直跟邻居们打听\N{\fs12}are walking around talking to the neighbors
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  你要知道  整栋楼里的人都在说\N{\fs12}and, you know, like, people in the building are talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我是如何像利波拉斯一样和男人进进出出\N{\fs12}how I'm like Liberace with the men coming in and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,完全是没有的事\N{\fs12}lt's totally untrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的私生活是属于你自己的\N{\fs12}Well, your private life is your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是\N{\fs12}Yeah, of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你在你的弟弟们面前注意言行举止\N{\fs12}As long as you conduct yourself appropriately in front of your brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟弟们都知道我是同性恋  好吗\N{\fs12}My brothers know that I'm gay, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fs12}lt doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 你说的好吧是什么意思\N{\fs12}- Okay. - Whadaya mean, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想帮我  我可以直接找一个真正的律师\N{\fs12}You know if you're not into this, l can just go get a real lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我男朋友就是一个很厉害的律师\N{\fs12}My boyfriend's an expensive lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想因为这些小事打扰他\N{\fs12}l just don't feel like bothering him with something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果你想找人换了我  那就换吧\N{\fs12}Right. Well, if you want to replace me, then just replace me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,别怕伤了我的感情\N{\fs12}Don't bother sparing my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  如果你能解决这个问题  我也可以不找他\N{\fs12}Look... if you think you can handle this, l won't call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  呃  很抱歉  关于我爸爸的事\N{\fs12}Hey, um... Sorry about that... l mean, with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,说来话长\N{\fs12}lt's kind of a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fs12}lt's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不说这个  听着  我有一个想法\N{\fs12}Anyway, listen, l, uh... l have this idea about, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也许可以和你父亲的公司开展一些合作\N{\fs12}maybe setting up a relationship with your father's firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 和你的公司  - 合作\N{\fs12}- With your firm. - Relationship?
