Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得  他是一个好孩子  我在努力帮助他而已\N{\fs12}l mean, he's a good kid. I'm... trying to help him out, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当然理解\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说  这整件事  我不知道从何说起\N{\fs12}l mean, this is, uh... I mean, the whole thing... I don't know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  你不需要跟我解释的\N{\fs12}Jake, you don't need to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不是同性恋\N{\fs12}Look, I'm not gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰克  - 我真的不是\N{\fs12}- Jake... - I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我为现在的一切付出了太多\N{\fs12}I've worked too hard for something like this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,太努力  去避免人们说我是什么死同志\N{\fs12}Way too hard... to have people... talking about me like I'm some kind of faggot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是  只是不能让周围的人这样议论我\N{\fs12}l... I just... l can't have it around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就是  真的不能  - 没关系的\N{\fs12}- I just... I just... I can't. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.07,0:22:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的只是偶尔一次\N{\fs12}l mean, it's just once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道  这并不关乎爱情或者是其他什么\N{\fs12}You know, it's not like... It's not romantic or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都与我无关的  杰克\N{\fs12}lt's not my business, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,跟卢卡斯的这件事  是大概一个月之前的了\N{\fs12}lt just kinda happened about a month ago... with Lucas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,匹兹堡是一个小地方\N{\fs12}Pittsburgh's a small town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fs12}lt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是的\N{\fs12}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么进来的\N{\fs12}How'd you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.37,0:23:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,进来并不难\N{\fs12}lt's not hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的  只是需要一点钱\N{\fs12}l just... I just need a few bucks, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要多少\N{\fs12}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就几千美金\N{\fs12}Just a few thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是  需要去买一些处方药\N{\fs12}l just... I need to pay for some prescription drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我得了该死的癌症  药都很贵  真的\N{\fs12}l got this damn cancer thing happening and... pills are expensive, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝  我不知道你怎么会这么害怕我\N{\fs12}l don't know why l scare you so much, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是你的爸爸啊\N{\fs12}l mean, I'm just your daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:23:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧\N{\fs12}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.51,0:24:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的爸爸啊\N{\fs12}I'm just your daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,请拿着你的钱  离开这里\N{\fs12}Please take your money and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.09,0:24:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁给了卢卡斯请保姆的钱\N{\fs12}Who gave Lucas the money for the babysitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.92,0:24:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,家里的一个朋友\N{\fs12}A family friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他在场吗\N{\fs12}ls he or she present?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有在\N{\fs12}Not available, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.37,0:24:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在作出决定之前我需要先跟他沟通一下\N{\fs12}Well, I'll need to speak with him before I make a ruling.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么一定要这样\N{\fs12}Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.73,0:24:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}l beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,法官阁下 你让我们想出一个解决方案\N{\fs12}Your Honor you asked us to come up! with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.57,0:24:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他雇了一个保姆\N{\fs12}He hired a babysitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.88,0:24:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,卢卡斯现在需要更多的钱  那两个月后又会发生什么\N{\fs12}And what happens two months from now when Lucas needs more money?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.38,0:24:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要确定卢卡斯自己可以解决这个问题\N{\fs12}We have to trust that Lucas can come up with it on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.23,0:24:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我还是要跟那个人谈一下\N{\fs12}Well, I'd still like to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.83,0:24:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,达森法官  您给卢卡斯提了要求 他也按照要求做了\N{\fs12}Judge Damsen, you gave Lucas a directive. He followed that through.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.87,0:24:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  不要打断我\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin, do not interrupt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.54,0:24:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  我们还是别牵扯无关的人了吧\N{\fs12}I'm sorry. Let's not make this about a third party.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.21,0:24:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,法尔先生  这是你的最后一次机会\N{\fs12}Mr. Farr, this is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.42,0:24:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.05,0:25:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你的新律师给我爸爸打电话了\N{\fs12}Your new lawyer called my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.33,0:25:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说了\N{\fs12}l heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.51,0:25:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  杰德  这太荒谬了\N{\fs12}Come on, Jed. This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.26,0:25:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在说这九万三千美元\N{\fs12}We're talking about ninety-three thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.21,0:25:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你更应该跟我的律师谈\N{\fs12}You should probably be talking to my lawyer about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.61,0:25:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以达成一致的\N{\fs12}We can be nice to a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.08,0:25:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你在吓唬我吗\N{\fs12}Are you threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.46,0:25:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不能得出解决措施\N{\fs12}lf we can't work something out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.15,0:25:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就会起诉\N{\fs12}we're gonna have to sue,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.69,0:25:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,之后你就得付一大笔律师费\N{\fs12}and you're gonna end up spending a lot of money on legal fees
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.90,0:25:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,跟付给我们的几乎一样多\N{\fs12}as well as paying us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.57,0:25:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲每年收了我六万五千美元的信托管理费\N{\fs12}Your father charges me sixty-five thousand dollars a year to oversee my Trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.18,0:25:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是六万五千美元啊\N{\fs12}Sixty-five thousand dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.42,0:25:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就只是为了审查银行账单  为了一个月打两个电话\N{\fs12}to review bank statements... to make two phone calls a month--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.91,0:25:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这两件事还都是烦人的事\N{\fs12}both of which are annoying--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.35,0:25:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只会告诉我  我不能做什么\N{\fs12}to tell me what I can't do,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.73,0:25:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,提醒我  我是个白痴  而我爸是个天才\N{\fs12}that I'm an idiot, that my father was a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.78,0:25:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸就是那样的人  你是知道他的\N{\fs12}Well, that's just my father. You know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.63,0:25:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我破产了\N{\fs12}I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.10,0:25:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,俱乐部的事都要烦死我了\N{\fs12}The Club is killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.25,0:25:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你欠了多少钱\N{\fs12}How much money do you owe?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.75,0:25:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多两百万美元\N{\fs12}Almost two million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.32,0:25:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真的破产了  撤诉吧  让我们来帮你\N{\fs12}lf you're broke, drop the suit. Let us help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.68,0:25:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我付不起\N{\fs12}l can't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.72,0:26:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,能试的我都试过了\N{\fs12}I've tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.90,0:26:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我也给朋友们打电话了\N{\fs12}I've called friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.60,0:26:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至跟银行谈过\N{\fs12}l talked to the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.48,0:26:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是还是没有钱\N{\fs12}l just don't have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.55,0:26:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,经历过强奸指控后  我被解雇了\N{\fs12}After the rape charge, I got fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.73,0:26:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经透支了\N{\fs12}l was already over-extended.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.42,0:26:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,私人学校  新房子\N{\fs12}Private school. New house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.99,0:26:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我也找不到工作  试想一下  谁会雇我呢\N{\fs12}Now I can't find a job. l mean, who's gonna hire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.39,0:26:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  他们为什么\N{\fs12}Why... why would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.47,0:26:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能会坐牢\N{\fs12}l might be going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.20,0:26:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历克斯  尼克和伯顿最关心的是什么\N{\fs12}Alex, what Nick and Burton are most concerned with
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.53,0:26:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是制定一些新的付款时间表\N{\fs12}is creating some kind of payment schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.25,0:26:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在仅剩的就是我的房子了\N{\fs12}Well, all I have left is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.40,0:26:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还有的妻子  她\N{\fs12}And my wife... she doesn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.21,0:26:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她并不知道关于我们经济状况的事情\N{\fs12}she doesn't know about my... about our financial situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.79,0:26:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我之前说能付给你们\N{\fs12}l know I told you I could pay you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.23,0:26:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只能是卖了我的房子  我还没有跟我妻子说\N{\fs12}but to do that I'd have to sell my house, and I haven't told my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.05,0:26:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我现在不想继续这个话题了\N{\fs12}All right, look... I'd like to... not continue this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.59,0:26:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你明天在法庭上会有一场硬仗  我们在审判之后再说这件事吧\N{\fs12}You got a tough day in court tomorrow. Why don't we take this up after the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.88,0:26:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  我会付给你钱的\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin, I'll pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.63,0:27:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证  我会付给你的\N{\fs12}l promise, I'll pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.72,0:27:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.38,0:27:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我需要准备明天的开庭了\N{\fs12}Well... I have to prepare for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.22,0:27:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  太感谢你了  赛迪\N{\fs12}Yeah, thanks, Sadie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.54,0:27:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,生意难做啊\N{\fs12}Tough business.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.53,0:27:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  你去见杰克了吗\N{\fs12}Nick, have you seen Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.81,0:27:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.77,0:27:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,木星高尔夫球公司的人在会议室等他\N{\fs12}Those guys from Jupiter Golf are waiting in the conference room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.82,0:27:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我给他打电话了  但是没有人接\N{\fs12}l called Jake's cell phone. He's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.93,0:27:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.44,0:27:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,克鲁切克先生  很抱歉让您等了这么久\N{\fs12}Mr. Kruczek. Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.77,0:27:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  不急  杰克呢\N{\fs12}Oh, no. No worries. Where's Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.53,0:28:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个紧急客户  他很快就会回来\N{\fs12}Uh, client emergency. He'll be... he'll be back pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.09,0:28:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我仔细看了你的代言合同\N{\fs12}So uh... l, uh, read over your endorsement agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.95,0:28:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好的开始\N{\fs12}lt's a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.74,0:28:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,您想来点咖啡吗\N{\fs12}You want a coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.34,0:28:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还是水或者苏打\N{\fs12}Water? Soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.49,0:28:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不需要了  谢谢\N{\fs12}No, we're good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.61,0:28:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那么第一个问题就是版税的问题了\N{\fs12}Okay. Well, first issue is the royalty payout.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.39,0:28:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的助理律师正在整理一些可行的方案\N{\fs12}Uh, my paralegal is putting together some comparables right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.38,0:28:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  关于奥克芒\N{\fs12}So... Oakmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.49,0:28:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我正努力调整一下日程\N{\fs12}I'm trying to clear my schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.18,0:28:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,从一个在斯克兰顿的\N{\fs12}Have to extricate myself from a wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.75,0:28:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,婚礼中抽身\N{\fs12}in Scranton... of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.29,0:28:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候开球\N{\fs12}So what time is tee-off?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.60,0:28:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 七点零六  - 好的\N{\fs12}- 7:06. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.39,0:28:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你的差点指数是多少\N{\fs12}What's your handicap?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.03,0:28:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,差点指数  六\N{\fs12}Handicap. Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.37,0:28:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,六吗  那你可以和专业的一起玩了\N{\fs12}Six? You'll play with the pro, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.32,0:28:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们配不上你了\N{\fs12}You're outta my league.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这个  如果我能不用去那个婚礼的话\N{\fs12}Well, that's if I can get out of the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.88,0:28:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  我很理解  希望到时能见到你\N{\fs12}Of course, I understand. Hope to see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.52,0:28:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰德有信儿了吗  - 没有\N{\fs12}- Any word from Jake? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.21,0:28:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给他家打电话了吗  - 打了四次了\N{\fs12}- You try his apartment? - Four times.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.20,0:29:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,卢卡斯\N{\fs12}Lucas.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.19,0:29:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一点同志争执罢了\N{\fs12}A little bit of fag-bashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.79,0:29:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜杰德是想要证明他不是同性恋\N{\fs12}l guess Jake wanted to make a point that he's not gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.72,0:29:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  他在这吗\N{\fs12}Right. Is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.65,0:29:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没  他已经走了  他喝了很多\N{\fs12}No. He's gone. He... he was drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.08,0:29:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,冲进屋子\N{\fs12}He came into the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.39,0:29:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们聊了一会  我想我也说了一些气话\N{\fs12}We had some words. l said some stupid things, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.86,0:29:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  抱歉  我得收拾好然后去上班了\N{\fs12}So... uh... if you'll excuse me, l have to clean up and get to work.
