Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.87,0:40:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了\N{\fs12}Yeah. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.40,0:40:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,至于亚历克斯·凯勒的事儿  嗯\N{\fs12}As for Alex Kaller, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.36,0:40:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们也许可以做些什么\N{\fs12}l thought maybe we could work something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.32,0:40:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,赛迪胜诉了  他也给我们提点了\N{\fs12}lt's a win for Sadie and he brought Checkpoint to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.26,0:40:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一共十六万美元啊\N{\fs12}Ah... it's a hundred and sixty thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.33,0:40:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但是他已经打算卖掉房子了  爸爸\N{\fs12}Yeah, well, he's ready to sell his home, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.37,0:40:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们欠银行一百万美金哪\N{\fs12}Well, we owe the bank a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.78,0:40:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.32,0:40:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.64,0:40:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.98,0:40:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尽快让他付款\N{\fs12}We get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.16,0:40:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,赛迪\N{\fs12}Sadie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.02,0:40:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,祝贺你  干得漂亮\N{\fs12}Congratulations. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.35,0:40:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.57,0:40:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你能跟亚历克斯说  我理解卖掉房子还需要一段时间\N{\fs12}Can you tell Alex that, you know, I know it may take some time to sell the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.71,0:40:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fs12}lt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.83,0:40:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  我会转告他  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Right. I will. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.08,0:40:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,格雷琴\N{\fs12}Gretchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.07,0:40:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 木星公司的人在吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- The guys from Jupiter Golf in there? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.95,0:40:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那杰德呢  - 我没看见他\N{\fs12}- What about Jake? - I didn't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.34,0:41:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,假设一个球跑过了第七果岭  对吧\N{\fs12}So supposedly, a turkey ran across the seventh green, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.54,0:41:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一秒钟之后  另一个球从后边追它\N{\fs12}A second later a fox comes bolting ou't after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.29,0:41:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,刚好超过了厄尼埃尔斯的球\N{\fs12}Goes right over Ernie Els' ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.17,0:41:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  尼克  - 你好\N{\fs12}- Hey, Nick. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.84,0:41:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  我来晚了\N{\fs12}Uh... sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.93,0:41:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的  我们正聊的开心\N{\fs12}No, it's okay. We're, uh... we're good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.07,0:41:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们正要开始  - 太好了\N{\fs12}- We're just getting started. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.35,0:41:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  是的  我们聊得很开心\N{\fs12}Yeah. Yeah. We're... we're good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.88,0:41:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs12}Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.67,0:41:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是  呃\N{\fs12}I just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.10,0:41:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是  嗯\N{\fs12}I-- I just, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.46,0:41:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  需要我接手吗\N{\fs12}Uh, Jake, you want me to take over?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.90,0:41:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  我们接着聊聊版税结构的问题\N{\fs12}No, let's just... let's just talk about royalty structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.74,0:41:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,薪水应该是未来版税的预付款\N{\fs12}Salary should be an advance against future royalties.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.00,0:41:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们想要百分之三  我减到了百分之二\N{\fs12}Now they wanted three percent. I got 'em down to two percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.29,0:41:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我觉得每个人都能满意了\N{\fs12}I think everyone's gonna be happy all the way around.
